{"lastModified":1776234323152,"uri":"c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Australia\n\nLook no further and settle for no less when you see this stunning 35m superyacht. She gleams as she cruises Australasia & South Pacific. Built in 2015 by the famous Sunseeker Predator 115. Her exterior and interior are also designed by Sunseeker. It will be obvious to everyone when they see how stylish and proudly she presents herself.\n\nAccommodating up to 10 guests with five cabins, shared amongst two large doubles and two twin rooms. Each room holds a similar theme. They are light and are furnished to a very high standard. The raised beds show just how high the ceilings are and create room for extra storage. The fabrics are silk and satin with pops of colour using cushions and throws. The furniture in the rooms are light wood and surround the room. The master ensuite bathroom is large with a jet spa bath tub and shower. The gloss wood continues in here. \n\nLeading upstairs on gloss tiled staircase, the lounge and dining room can be found on the main deck.\n\nRASCAL's lounge room is surrounded with large windows allowing a lot of natural light. She has a lounge area with a mirrored square table and cream leather sofas. It is an idea space for using the onboard entertainment she has. Large flat screens can be viewed whilst enjoying the DVD player, Satcom, Satellite TV. It is a modern place to entertain. \nHer dining room table is mirrored and can seat up to 8 guests easily. Mirrored detail on the wall reflects and gives the impression of space. \n\nHer deck area is decked in light teak wood. Further entertaining takes places outside on comfortable white sofas round funky burnt orange tables. Here is the bar area completely white and crisps with tall bar stools and again great use of burnt orange cushions. It is bright and refreshing. Here guests can enjoy all the beautiful views. \n\nShe also has onboard an outdoor jacuzzi with an adjoined with a large cushioned lounge area. It is completely padded with a soft white fabric that is slightly patterned, perfect to dry off after a relaxing dip. \n\nHer onboard toys and tenders include seabob, jet ski, snorkelling and fishing gear, towable and inflatable toys. She also has Williams 505 Diesel jet Tender, RINA commercial and MCA LY3(short range) in lieu of standard.\n\n","blueprint":{"name":"RASCAL","images":["/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::abc962f0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::b53be790-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c62cc1f0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c62c9ae0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c62e6fa0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c63155d0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c62ee4d0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c6317ce0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c6312ec0-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5cae6f9-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::c62ee4d1-3dbd-11ef-ae79-67157891845d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8864389904::vessel::d5ca